                                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 blog-content">
                                    <div class="media-body">
                                    <h5><b>Bathrooms</b></h5>
                                    <p>Showers, bathtubs, sinks, drains – Mr. Speedy handles it all. If there’s a leak, we’ll fix it. If a drain is obstructed and won’t flow, we’ll clean it out and remove the obstruction. If a bathroom fixture needs repair, we can make it right again. If it can’t be repaired, we can replace it – our vans are stocked with quality parts and fixtures. Our plumbing technicians will explain the different options open to you, and will advise you on the best way to proceed.</p> 
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media-body">
                                    <h5><b>Faucet and Pipe Repair</b></h5>
                                    <p>Even the best faucets, fixtures and pipes eventually wear out with extended use. We can repair or replace any faucet, fixture or pipe in your home or place of business. We are familiar with all types of pipes, including copper and PVC/Plastic. And we carry the latest brands of quality faucets, including Price Pfister, Delta and Moen. Your plumbing tech can give you more advice and help you select the right fixtures.</p> 
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media-body">
                                    <h5><b>Toilets</b></h5>
                                    <p>A leaky or defective toilet can cause you to waste a lot of precious water. And a non-functioning toilet can quickly become a health hazard. We repair leaky/defective toilets and get them running smoothly again. If it needs replacing, we provide sales and installation of all major brands of toilets in a variety of models. To save money on your water bills, we suggest you look into installing a new low-flow toilet flush system: these new systems have two flush settings – one for liquid waste, one for solid waste and toilet paper. These new low-flow systems use less water and save you money on your water bills. We carry the leading brands of toilets, including Kohler and American Standard.</p> 
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media-body">
                                    <h5><b>Electronic Leak Detection</b></h5>
                                    <p>Pinpointing the exact location of a leak can be very difficult. Mr. Speedy has an array of the most sophisticated electronic leak detection devices that can identify a leak even if it is beneath a concrete slab, deep underground, or even behind a wall. We only start to dig when we know exactly where the leak is. We also have equipment to detect a gas leak on your property.</p> 
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media-body">
                                    <h5><b>Installations With Best Warranty</b></h5>
                                    <p>Our professional drain-cleaning and plumbing services include the installation of water heaters, garbage disposal units, showers, toilets, sinks and tubs. We carry a huge range of tools and quality replacement parts and fixtures in our vans. We are certified distributors and installers of the leading brands of water heaters, including Bradford White and Rheem.</p> 
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="media-body">
                                    <h5><b>Underground Pipe Replacement</b></h5>
                                    <p>We are experts a t repairing or replacing underground pipes which have deteriorated due to rust or by underground tree roots intruding into the pipes. We carry the latest in “trenchless technology” from Perma-Liner Industries Inc. These sophisticated tools allow us to reline or replace underground plumbing pipes and sewer lines without the need to do too much intrusive digging.</p> 
